---

<Base
	title="RIA Cybersecurity Services"
	description="Adelia Risk delivers expert RIA cybersecurity services for SEC-registered advisors — from vCISO support to exam-ready documentation."
>
	<Hero
		title="RIA Cybersecurity Services for Wealth Management Firms"
		subtitle='Stop worrying about wire fraud, SEC examinations, and "what if something happens to client data." We handle it.'
		ctaLabel="Get Your Free RIA Cybersecurity Assessment"
		ctaHref="#"
		align="center"
	/>

	<section class="ar-section" id="intro">
		<div class="ar-container-narrow" style="text-align: center;">
			<p class="ar-intro-lead">
				Adelia Risk is a cybersecurity firm that handles RIA cybersecurity services for SEC-registered
				advisors and wealth management firms. We build your security program, manage your tools, and
				<a href="#">get you examination-ready</a>. We've helped RIAs go from "we think we're secure" to
				confidently passing SEC examinations without losing their minds (or their clients).
			</p>
			<div class="ar-intro-cta">
				<a href="#why-adelia" class="ar-btn ar-btn-outline">See How We Work</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<TestimonialCarousel
		eyebrow="What Our Clients Say"
		title="What Our Clients Say"
		titleAccent="About Our RIA Cybersecurity Services"
		testimonials={testimonials}
	/>

	<IconFeatureGrid
		title="You're Not a Cybersecurity Expert"
		subtitle="The four things RIAs say when they explain why they haven't built a real cybersecurity program. Here's why each one misses the point."
		features={objections}
		columns={2}
	/>

	<TargetSection
		eyebrow="Why RIAs Are In The Crosshairs"
		title="You Have a Target on Your Back. Here's Why."
		body="RIAs and wealth management firms are among the most targeted businesses in the country because they control over $145 trillion in assets. You aren't targeted because you're doing something wrong. You're targeted because you're doing something valuable."
		listTitle="You Have Everything Hackers Want"
		items={hackersWant}
		footer="A single successful RIA cyberattack can yield more than dozens of attacks on regular businesses. Hackers know this."
		backgroundImage="https://adeliarisk.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/ChatGPT-Image-Jun-16-2025-10_41_43-AM-1.jpg"
	/>

	<ComparisonBlock
		eyebrow="Asymmetric Risk"
		title="You're Easier to Attack Than Banks"
		subtitle="Banks spend millions on security. Most RIAs are running with the bare minimum. Here's the gap hackers exploit."
		left={bigBanks}
		right={yourRia}
	/>

	<SecSection
		eyebrow="Regulatory Pressure"
		title="The SEC Is Watching"
		paragraphs={[
			"The SEC created a new Cyber and Emerging Technologies Unit (CETU) in February 2025. One of its priority areas is \"regulated entities' compliance with cybersecurity rules and regulations, including rules relating to the protection of customer information.\"",
			"SEC examinations can result in deficiency letters if your cybersecurity program doesn't meet expectations. That can mean enforcement actions, fines, and reputational damage. Our RIA cybersecurity services get you prepared.",
		]}
		listTitle="What SEC examiners look for"
		items={secWatchFor}
	/>

	<ComparisonBlock
		eyebrow="Know The Difference"
		title="IT Support and Cybersecurity Are Different Jobs"
		subtitle="Your IT provider is great at keeping the lights on. RIA cybersecurity is a different discipline entirely."
		left={itProvider}
		right={riaCyber}
		footnote="Our vCISO RIA security team works alongside your IT provider. They handle the tech. We double-check the security. Most of our clients keep their existing IT relationships."
		dark
	/>

	<div id="why-adelia">
		<IconFeatureGrid
			eyebrow="Why Wealth Management Firms Choose Adelia for RIA Cybersecurity Services"
			title="An RIA cybersecurity partner, not a vendor"
			subtitle="Four things that separate us from general-purpose cybersecurity consultants and hourly IT providers."
			features={reasons}
			columns={2}
		/>
	</div>

	<VideoEmbed
		eyebrow="See The Model"
		title="How Our Virtual CISOs Work With RIA Clients"
		subtitle="A short walkthrough of how Adelia Risk's vCISO team partners with wealth management firms to build security programs and pass SEC examinations."
		videoId="-Ich21VoCTo"
	/>

	<FeatureGrid
		eyebrow="Beyond the Base Program"
		title="Maybe you need more from a Virtual CISO?"
		subtitle="Our RIA cybersecurity services aren't one-size-fits-all. Some virtual CISOs offer the same program to everyone — and sometimes that's overkill. We'll help you decide if and when any of these additional solutions are needed."
		items={extras}
	/>

	<StatsRow
		eyebrow="Proven Cybersecurity Results"
		title="Real outcomes our RIA clients have seen"
		subtitle="Three representative engagements and where they landed."
		stats={results}
		dark
	/>

	<CtaBand
		eyebrow="RIA Cybersecurity That Grows With You"
		title="Let's book a consultation"
		subtitle="Prices start at a few hundred dollars a month for small clients and scale competitively for larger and more complex companies. Let's book a RIA cybersecurity services consultation to show how we can help."
		ctaLabel="Book a Consultation"
		ctaHref="#"
	/>

	<FAQAccordion
		eyebrow="Frequently Asked"
		title="RIA Cybersecurity Questions Answered"
		subtitle="The questions wealth management firms ask us most often when they start evaluating a new cybersecurity program."
		faqs={faqs}
	/>

	<CityList
		eyebrow="Nationwide Coverage"
		title="RIA Cybersecurity Services Nationwide"
		paragraphs={[
			"Adelia Risk provides RIA cybersecurity services to SEC-registered investment advisors and wealth management firms across the United States. Whether you're based in New York, California, Texas, Florida, or anywhere in between, our virtual CISO model delivers the same security coverage.",
			"Our clients include independent RIAs, multi-family offices, broker-dealers, and hybrid advisors managing assets from $100 million to over $10 billion. We know the security challenges wealth management firms face. We've built our services to address them.",
		]}
		listLabel="Service areas include:"
		cities={cities}
		mapImage="https://adeliarisk.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/map-new.jpg"
		mapAlt="USA map showing Adelia Risk nationwide RIA cybersecurity coverage"
	/>

	<CtaBand
		eyebrow="Ready When You Are"
		title="Protect Your Wealth Management Firm with our RIA Cybersecurity Services"
		subtitle="Talk to a vCISO who specializes in RIAs. We'll walk through your current setup, tell you exactly where you stand, and show you what it would cost to close the gaps."
		ctaLabel="Book Your Free Assessment"
		ctaHref="#"
	/>
</Base>

<style>
	.ar-intro-lead {
		font-family: var(--font-heading);
		font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 2.3vw, 1.75rem);
		line-height: 1.45;
		color: var(--color-text);
		margin: 0 0 2rem;
		font-weight: 500;
	}

	.ar-intro-lead :global(a) {
		color: var(--color-blue);
		border-bottom: 2px solid currentColor;
		transition: color 180ms ease;
	}

	.ar-intro-lead :global(a:hover) {
		color: var(--color-blue-hover);
	}

	.ar-intro-cta {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
	}
</style>
